## Requirements

| Dependency | Version |
|---|---|
| Python | ≥ 3.12 |
| PyTorch | 2.8.0 (CUDA 12.8 recommended) |
| PyTorch Geometric | ≥ 2.3.0 |
| Transformers | ≥ 4.36.0 |
| Accelerate | ≥ 0.26.0 |

See [`pyproject.toml`](https://github.com/RingBDStack/pygfm/blob/main/pyproject.toml) on GitHub for the full dependency specification.

